<h2>Thank you for being here</h2>
<p>We all arrive to therapy for different reasons. Sometimes it is just one traumatic situation, sometimes it is an accumulation, sometimes there is no specific trauma you feel happened and yet life doesn&rsquo;t feel like what it could be.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
